summary: This document is an email chain from September 29, 2019, concerning follow-up information from an interview. It involves a contractor passing on pictures and contact information (a middle school directory page with a phone number and address) related to an individual, likely a witness or victim, for investigative purposes. The document is subject to a protective order.

persons.name: Contractor
persons.context: The sender of the initial email, who is following up on interview information and sending pictures believed to be of a person of interest, including one from a time associated with 'the ranch'.

events.title: Follow-up Information Exchange

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated September 29, 2019, regarding follow-up information from an interview.
It references pictures, one believed to be a photo of an individual and another from a time associated with 'the ranch'.
It includes a middle school directory page showing a phone number and address for an individual, with the note that the number remained the same through high school.
The document is explicitly subject to a protective order covering specific paragraphs (7, 8, 9, 10, 15, and 17).
The correspondence is marked as confidential and subject to attorney-client privilege or similar protections.
